---

### 4. What Content is Rendered Inside the Container

The container renders a **two-view post gallery system**:

**GRID VIEW (default):**
- 3-column grid on desktop (2 columns on mobile)
- Each card shows:
  - Thumbnail image (4:3 aspect ratio)
  - Post title (truncated to 32 characters)
  - Preview text (first 50 characters)
  - Privacy icon (public/private)
  - Settings menu (3-dot icon)

**LIST VIEW (toggled via button):**
- Full-width cards stacked vertically
- Each card shows:
  - Large thumbnail image (max 240px height)
  - Post title (truncated to 55 characters)
  - Full preview text
  - Author avatar with name, date, and privacy status
  - Settings menu

**Additional Features:**
- Infinite scroll with intersection observer
- View mode toggle button (grid/list icons)
- Post count badge in header
- Settings dropdown with options:
  - Delete journal
  - Edit journal (or edit caption for reposts)
  - Change privacy (public ↔ private)
- Delete confirmation dialog
- Success message on deletion
- Loading spinner during deletion
- Verified badge display for OG/Legend users
- Glowing avatar rings for special users

